26 Community College.
27 (ii) 1. The review and approval of the Board of Public Works
28 shall be required for the following types of contracts with a value that exceeds $1,000,000
29 for a University or $500,000 for Baltimore City Community College:
30 A. capital improvements; and
31 B. services.
32 2. In its review of a contract for services or capital
33 improvements with a value that exceeds $1,000,000, the Board of Public Works may request

